race.description: Sportsbet Same Race Multi Rating 0 - 56 Handicap
race.comment: BLUE SPECIAL (1) was quickly back on track beaten a whisker over a miler at Strathalbyn. Draws the rail again and a 2kg claimer is aboard today. Placed to advantage and he can go one better. GUMERACHA CRACKER (6) was within range in the same contest, running her best race. In good hands and may go on with it now. BYWATERS ROAD (10) just missed twice before a plain effort at Murray Bridge. Has an awkward gate but this suits better and his best figures measure up. Can do a lot better. FLEURIEU FLIPPER (4) got too far back at favourite at The Bridge and may be worth another chance on the 8-day return.
